== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度僅7%，基於132條評論，平均分為2.9/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771422158/ |title=Mother's Day (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-06-25 |archive-date=2016-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613110751/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771422158 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到18分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/mothers-day-2016|title=Mother's Day reviews|website=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-06-13|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610182814/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/mothers-day-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>，差評居多。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/keanu-the-jungle-book-mothers-day-weekend-box-office-1201746538/ |title=''Jungle Book'' Still Hot In Third Weekend With $35M-$36M; ''Mother's Day'' Has Edge Over ''Keanu'' |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-10-28 |archive-date=2016-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430115024/https://deadline.com/2016/04/keanu-the-jungle-book-mothers-day-weekend-box-office-1201746538/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國及加拿大，首映週末有3,035個劇院播映。最終，電影在北美地區票房總額為3250萬美元，其他地區收入1130萬美元，全球總計4380萬美元<ref name="Numbers"/>。

